```latex
\begin{IEEEbiography}[{\includegraphics[width=1in,height=1.25in,clip,keepaspectratio]{fig/tiankanghui.png}}]{Kanghui Tian}
Kanghui Tian is currently an undergraduate student at Sun Yat-sen University (SYSU), Shenzhen, China. He will pursue the Ph.D. degree at Fudan University. His research interests include multimodal large language models and long video understanding.
\end{IEEEbiography}
```

IEEEbiography 这一句的 `{Kanghui Tian}` 本来就是放“姓名”的位置（相当于标题），正文第一句通常不再重复姓名。你可以改成不重复姓名的写法，例如：

```latex
\begin{IEEEbiography}[{\includegraphics[width=1in,height=1.25in,clip,keepaspectratio]{fig/tiankanghui.png}}]{Kanghui Tian}
He is currently an undergraduate student at Sun Yat-sen University (SYSU), Shenzhen, China, and will pursue the Ph.D. degree at Fudan University. His research interests include multimodal large language models and long video understanding.
\end{IEEEbiography}
```

如果你更想保持原例子风格（“received the B.S. ... in YEAR”），也可以写成：

```latex
\begin{IEEEbiography}[{\includegraphics[width=1in,height=1.25in,clip,keepaspectratio]{fig/tiankanghui.png}}]{Kanghui Tian}
He is currently pursuing the B.S. degree at Sun Yat-sen University (SYSU), Shenzhen, China, and will pursue the Ph.D. degree at Fudan University. His research interests include multimodal large language models and long video understanding.
\end{IEEEbiography}
```
